trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click"></xref> event of an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click"> </xref> 의 이벤트는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control is clicked.

To allow a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object to raise the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event, you must first set either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to `HotSpotMode.PostBack`.
trans-unit.target: 허용 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>를 발생 시키는 개체의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>이벤트를 먼저 설정 해야는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성을 `HotSpotMode.PostBack`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To control the actions programmatically that are performed when a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, provide an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: 프로그래밍 방식으로 다시 게시를 수행 하는 동작을 제어할 수 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>는 클릭에 대 한 이벤트 처리기를 제공는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property stores a string that is associated with the behavior of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object when clicked.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>의 동작과 연결 되는 문자열을 저장 하는 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>클릭 했을 때 개체.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: This string is passed in the ImageMapEventArgs event data when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: ImageMapEventArgs 이벤트 데이터에서이 문자열은 전달 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>를 클릭 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>
